META
    esp_version `1.0`
    author `test-suite`
    date `2025-10-02`
    severity `high`
    platform `linux`
    description `behavior testing`
    control_framework `CIS`
    control `5.2.1-5.2.6`
    esp_scan_id `behavior_testing`
    criticality `high`
    tags `linux,ssh,security`
META_END

DEF
    OBJECT test_file
        path `/etc/passwd`
        behavior recursive_scan max_depth 3
    OBJECT_END

    STATE has_content
        content string contains `root`
    STATE_END

    CRI AND
        CTN file_content
            TEST all all
            OBJECT_REF test_file
            STATE_REF has_content
        CTN_END
    CRI_END
DEF_END
